Package fr.n7.saceca.u3du.model.ai

Interface Summary
AI The Interface AI.
SimulationListener The listener interface for receiving Simulation events.
WorldObjectFilter An interface to filter world objects.
 

Class Summary
AIImpl The implantation of the AI interface.
EntitiesFactory A factory to create "entities" (i.e. reactive objects and agents).
EntitiesFactoryMaterials A class to gather elements required by the entities factory to run.
Internal A class which is dynamically built using common models to contain the names of the properties.
Internal.Agent A container for fields common to all the agent models.
Internal.Object A container for fields common to all the world object models.
IOManager The Class IOManager manages the IO streams of the AI.
Simulation This class simulates a world evolving in time, with agents and reactive objects inside.
World The Class World contains all the world objects.
 

Enum Summary
Visibility The enumeration of possible visibilities.
